data.description: NEW ROOF PRIOR TO CLOSE + $5,000 BUYER CREDIT! The freshly painted interior and brand new carpets make this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home move-in ready! The generously sized primary suite features two closets and an ensuite bath. The guest bathroom provides an ADA accessible shower. Front exterior woodwork has been replaced & painted, and the front has been landscaped. The backyard features a large stained deck, a covered porch, and a solid fence that creates the perfect setting for outdoor enjoyment. Just steps away is Porter Elementary & a walking trail that leads you to the serene Palos Verdes Lake. This charming residence is on a quiet street and offers a central location with easy access to highways and nearby stores. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours!
